item.title: Dub by the Ocean - JonnyHillstrom [Reggae Dub] ~ anything you would change/add?
item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
Lol this is awesome. I have no idea how much of this is Auxy but frankly I don’t care. I think this resonates with me especially because I’ve been listening to a ton of jungle and ragga jungle which owes A LOT to this genre.

I don’t think I’d change anything, the vocals might be a little loud (they almost sound overdriven a little) - I think everything else seems ok.

Real nice man
